  <div class="col-md-8 mb-4 mb-md-0">
      <h1 class="h2">
          <span>Quaker Leader Diane Randall Named Gender Champion in Nuclear Policy</span>

      </h1>
  <div class="mb-2 d-print-none">
  <a href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A//www.fcnl.org/updates/2021-02/quaker-leader-diane-randall-named-gender-champion-nuclear-policy" target="_blank" class="mr-3 share-link" title="Share this page on Facebook"><i class="fab fa-facebook-f"></i><span class="sr-only">Share this page on Facebook</span></a><a href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?url=https%3A//www.fcnl.org/updates/2021-02/quaker-leader-diane-randall-named-gender-champion-nuclear-policy&amp;via=fcnl" target="_blank" class="mr-3 share-link" title="Share this page on Twitter"><i class="fab fa-twitter"></i><span class="sr-only">Share this page on Twitter</span></a><a href="mailto:?subject=Quaker%20Leader%20Diane%20Randall%20Named%20Gender%20Champion%20in%20Nuclear%20Policy&amp;body=https%3A//www.fcnl.org/updates/2021-02/quaker-leader-diane-randall-named-gender-champion-nuclear-policy" target="_blank" class="mr-3 share-link" title="Email this page"><i class="fal fa-envelope"></i><span class="sr-only">Email this page</span></a><a href="/updates/2021-02/quaker-leader-diane-randall-named-gender-champion-nuclear-policy#print" onclick="window.print(); return false;" class="mr-3 share-link" title="Print this page"><i class="fal fa-print"></i><span class="sr-only">Print this page</span></a>
</div>
<div class="meta byline h4 font-weight-normal mb-2 text-nocase">By&nbsp;<a href="/people/timothy-mchugh" hreflang="en">Timothy McHugh</a>&ensp;|&ensp;<span >February 4, 2021</span>
</div>




      <ul class="font-sans-serif small list-unstyled list-inline">
              <li class="list-inline-item"><i class="fal fa-angle-double-right fa-lg text-dream"></i>&ensp;<a href="/issues/nuclear-weapons" hreflang="en">Nuclear Weapons</a></li>
          </ul>
  

  </div>
  <div class="col-md-4 pull-down-xs">
        
    </div>
</div>
